{"tid":1838434,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】屈臣氏網店50個口罩賣＄49.9 逾六萬人排隊買","createTime":"2020-01-24T04:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T09:38:39.000Z","uid":40152,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c1ef0cf73568de027e226bc423be20c9981db5","tid":1838434,"uid":40152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Fv9Qyl65PBjnMedH3hD2Wg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200124a072554.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFv9Qyl65PBjnMedH3hD2Wg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200124a072554.jpg&h=6264d5cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎爆發，本港市民搶購口罩，有藥房更坐地起價。不過有網民指屈臣氏網上商店有口罩出售，並以良心價發售，導致網上商店出現排隊人龍。市民昨晚嘗試登入屈臣氏網店，發現有逾6萬個用戶，要預計一個多小時才可進入網上商店。<br />\n<br />\n消委會總幹事黃鳯嫺敦促藥房及商戶不要趁火打劫，要齊心協力維護公共衛生，又呼籲市民無需瘋狂搶購口罩，以免助長抬價的行為。<br />\n<br />\n黃鳯嫺表示，消委會本月初調查時發現有頗多口罩缺貨，價格亦有較多上落，之後價格及供應漸趨穩定。消委會又指，今早再到過上水店鋪了解口罩價格，發現每個普通成人外科口罩價格，由一元到數十元不等，少數店鋪亦有缺貨，不過口罩的價格幅度頗大，每個N95口罩索價30至78元不等，普通成人口罩由1元至18元不等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，消委會主席林定國則指，香港目前無價格管制法例，呼籲供應口罩的商戶應從公共健康角度出發，要考慮到社會責任問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1687740/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B1%88%E8%87%A3%E6%B0%8F%E7%B6%B2%E5%BA%9750%E5%80%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E8%B3%A3-49-9-%E9%80%BE%E5%85%AD%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%8E%92%E9%9A%8A%E8%B2%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1687740%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B1%2588%25E8%2587%25A3%25E6%25B0%258F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%25BA%259750%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E8%25B3%25A3-49-9-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%2585%25AD%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25B2%25B7&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXz2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=366e736c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1687740%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B1%2588%25E8%2587%25A3%25E6%25B0%258F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%25BA%259750%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E8%25B3%25A3-49-9-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%2585%25AD%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25B2%25B7&h=5b9b7eed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1687740/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B1%88%E8%87%A3%E6%B0%8F%E7%B6%B2%E5%BA%9750%E5%80%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E8%B3%A3-49-9-%E9%80%BE%E5%85%AD%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%8E%92%E9%9A%8A%E8%B2%B7</a>"},{"pid":"682ff2889820979cb5a3880e917bcf4d4603d7ad","tid":1838434,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:24:42.000Z","msg":"兩個文宣方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）將正苦對武漢肺炎既不作為link埋去為左搞散場運動（放任病人流入黎減少群鬥聚集）<br />\n2）林鄭掛住係瑞士向國際政治宣傳都唔理香港疫情萌芽"},{"pid":"5829f762aabb486def68816ccd0237ee1a289c35","tid":1838434,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:25:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"f9074dae637f81d4e761791d8280e648159a0db4","tid"